  "body": "## Problem \r\nWhen audio is in the composer in the preview stage, the keyboard can be opened by tapping on the composer. This allows data to be typed, which results in the audio being removed from the composer\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n1. Open any chat\r\n2. Start recording the audio\r\n3. Stop recording\r\n4. Tap on the composer\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe keyboard opens, even though there is audio in the composer.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/70a9bc1d-9a0e-4bb3-afe1-7c6e54b5f388\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe keyboard should not open when the audio is in the composer\r\n\r\n### ENV: \r\n- nightly [17 May 2023]\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n",
